{"type":"message","id":"20bf0496","parentId":"08f9e215","timestamp":"2026-07-21T01:00:00.253Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Tuesday, July 21st, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-07-21 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1784595600252}}
{"type":"message","id":"6694c8ef","parentId":"20bf0496","timestamp":"2026-07-21T01:03:20.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job reminder task. The user is reminding me of Cursor collaboration rules. Since this is a cron job trigger and the task says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, just silently confirm), I should just acknowledge and not send any message.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - this is a cron job that fires and delivers a summary. The instruction says \"Return your summary as plain text\" - but the note says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" which means \"no reply needed, just silently confirm.\"\n\nSince this is a daily reminder cron job about rules I've already been told, I should just confirm silently and not send any response. But the cron system expects a summary to be delivered automatically. Let me just provide a brief confirmation."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nCursor 协作规则已确认记住：\n1. 任务提交用 submit_task.py\n2. 确认回复用 confirm_write.py\n3. 查看队列用 --list\n4. 查看结果用 --results\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1784595600253}}
